# Docs — division of truth (canonical)

**Single source for doc boundaries.** Other rules/skills link here; do not duplicate the tables below.

Index: [`Docs/README.md`](../../Docs/README.md). Workflow: [`vibe-coding-workflow` SKILL](../skills/vibe-coding-workflow/SKILL.md).

**Editing `Docs/Archived/plans/`** — history only; sync checklist **N/A** unless fixing broken links.

---

## Primary home

| Document | Owns | Must NOT own |
|----------|------|--------------|
| **`Active-Plan.md`** | **All open `[ ]`** — queue, gates, hardening index | Diagrams, policy prose, changelogs |
| **`Wishlist.md`** | **S9–S21 + P-Sim/P-Slice + Backlog** staged `[ ]` only | Active sprint tasks, gates table, shipped sections |
| **`Archived-Plan.md`** | Completed stubs + § S1 implementation notes | Open tasks, full `[x]` checklists |
| **`EngineArchitecture.md`** | Diagrams, **locked policies**, risks, non-goals | `[ ]` tasks, sprint logs |
| **`README.md`** | Index + **Active now** (WIP pointer) | Task lists, gates, duplicate file maps |
| **`{name}_Plan.md` (roadmap)** | Design / steps for one topic | Queue duplicates |
| **`{name}_Plan.md` + `_Progress` (WIP)** | One in-flight task | Second WIP pair at `Docs/` root |

Closed epics live under `Docs/Archived/plans/` only.

---

## What to edit (minimize touch)

| Event | Edit | Do **not** edit |
|-------|------|-----------------|
| Open / close task | `Active-Plan.md` | Wishlist, README (unless WIP) |
| Task done | Stub → `Archived-Plan.md`; remove from Active-Plan | Wishlist, Architecture |
| Promote Wishlist → active | Add `[ ]` to Active-Plan; Wishlist → drop or index only | Gates in Wishlist |
| Vibe kickoff | `README.md` **Active now** + `{Plan}_Progress.md` | Active-Plan queue unless scope changed |
| Vibe close | Progress closeout → `Archived/plans/`; clear README **Active now** | EngineArchitecture unless policy |
| **Locked policy** (tree below) | `EngineArchitecture.md` + code/shaders | Wishlist |
| Deferred milestone | `Wishlist.md` only (S9–S21 / P-Sim) | Active-Plan |
| Gate met | `Active-Plan.md` gates row (✓) | Wishlist |

---

## Plan file types

| Type | `_Progress.md` | Count at `Docs/` root |
|------|----------------|------------------------|
| **Roadmap plan** | No until kickoff | Multiple OK |
| **Task WIP** | Required | **One pair max** |

---

## Locked policy? (decision tree)

1. Layer boundary moved? → **yes, policy**
2. Descriptor model changed? → **yes, policy**
3. Extract / record contract changed? → **yes, policy**
4. Transparent / Stage 2 depth rule changed? → **yes, policy**
5. Struct fields / bindings only → code + MSBuild; Architecture if (2) narrative shifts
6. Task done, no 1–4 → Active-Plan → Archived-Plan only

---

## Agent `@`

| Goal | `@` |
|------|-----|
| Next task | `Active-Plan.md` |
| Layer / policy | `EngineArchitecture.md` |
| WIP steps | `{Task}_Plan.md` + `_Progress.md` |
| Staged S9+ | `Wishlist.md` |
| History | `Archived-Plan.md` / `Archived/plans/` |

---

## Anti-patterns

- Gates / queue / open `[ ]` in Wishlist or README
- Same table in Active-Plan and Architecture
- `[x]` in Active-Plan or Wishlist
- Architecture edit on every task close
- Second WIP Plan+Progress pair at Docs root
- Shipped sprint checklists in Wishlist or Archived-Plan (use `Archived/plans/`)
